```

### Define a Configuration Schema

Next, define a configuration schema using `jsonschema`. This schema will specify the structure and constraints for the configuration files.

#### `my_project_manager/schemas/config_schema.json`

```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "core": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "config_file": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "log_level": {
          "type": "string",
          "enum": ["DEBUG", "INFO", "WARNING", "ERROR", "CRITICAL"]
        }
      },
      "required": ["config_file", "log_level"]
    },
    "plugins": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "compatible_plugin": {
          "type": "object",
          "properties": {
            "enabled": {
              "type": "boolean"
            },
            "timeout": {
              "type": "integer",
